description:
To use the Old Polish Jokes skill, ask:

"Alexa, launch polish joke"

Most jokes are of Question/Answer type. Quick one liners. Have fun! May not be appropriate for all ages.
exampleInteractions: Alexa, ask polish joke to tell me a Polish Joke
name: Old Polish Jokes
shortDescription: Tells "Old Polish Jokes" :) Just ask Alexa, "launch Polish Joke". May not be appropriate for all ages.
